## State entities (runtime cache)

```
┌──────────────────────────────────┐
│        StateManager               │
│──────────────────────────────────│
│ Keyed by: (StateId, VehicleRoute) │
│       or: (StateId, TourActivity) │
│                                   │
│ Stores computed values:           │
│  - load at each activity          │
│  - time slack                     │
│  - future picks/deliveries        │
│  - any custom state               │
└──────────────────────────────────┘
  Uses: StateId constants (static final instances)
  Note: values are cleared and recomputed after each ruin/recreate step
```

## Key cardinalities summary

| Relationship | Cardinality |
|---|---|
| VRP → Vehicle | 1 .. * |
| VRP → Job | 0 .. * |
| Vehicle → VehicleType | * .. 1 |
| VehicleRoute → Vehicle | * .. 1 |
| VehicleRoute → TourActivity | 1 .. * (ordered) |
| Shipment → Location | 2 (pickup + delivery) |
| Service/Pickup/Delivery → Location | 1 |
| Job → TimeWindow | 1 .. * |
| Job → Capacity | 1 |
| Vehicle → Skills, Job → Skills | 0..1 each (vehicle must cover job's required skills) |
